sequenceDiagram
autonumber
actor Owner as OwnerAdmin
actor Member as CandidateUser
participant Client as WebClient
participant Gateway as ApiGateway
participant OrgAuth as OrgProtectAuthorize
participant OrgCtrl as OrganizationController
participant MemberCtrl as MemberController
participant JoinCtrl as JoinApplicationController
participant OrgDb as MongoOrgMembership
participant RoleSync as RolePermissionSync
participant Notify as NotificationOrRealtime
Note over Owner,OrgDb: Tao organization
Owner->>Client: Tao to chuc moi
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/organizations
Gateway->>OrgAuth: Auth + route to org-service
OrgAuth-->>Gateway: pass
Gateway->>OrgCtrl: createOrganization
OrgCtrl->>OrgDb: Insert Organization + Membership(owner)
OrgCtrl->>OrgDb: Seed default Department/Channel
OrgCtrl->>RoleSync: ensureDefaultOrgRoles + sync owner
OrgCtrl->>Notify: emit org_created
OrgCtrl-->>Client: 201 Created
Note over Owner,Member: Moi thanh vien
Owner->>Client: Moi thanh vien vao org
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/organizations/:orgId/members
Gateway->>MemberCtrl: inviteMember
MemberCtrl->>OrgDb: Upsert membership pending
alt Da la thanh vien active
  MemberCtrl-->>Client: 409 conflict
else Moi hop le
  MemberCtrl->>Notify: emit invite event
  MemberCtrl-->>Client: 200/201
end
Note over Member,JoinCtrl: Nop don tham gia
Member->>Client: Gui don join application
Client->>Gateway: POST /api/organizations/:orgId/join-applications
Gateway->>JoinCtrl: submitApplication
JoinCtrl->>OrgDb: Validate schema + save pending
alt Reviewer approve
  JoinCtrl->>OrgDb: Create/activate membership
  JoinCtrl->>RoleSync: sync member role
  JoinCtrl->>Notify: send approved notification
  JoinCtrl-->>Client: 200 approved
else Reject/invalid
  JoinCtrl-->>Client: 400/403/409
end
